Gitorious Merge Request Monitor
- A simple service for following the status of Gitorious merge requests.

Currently supports reporting status over IRC.

Author: Jon Nordby <jononor@gmail.com>
License: GPLv3+
Website: https://github.com/jonnor/gitorious-mrq-monitor

== Dependencies ==
Python 2.x
Twisted
feedparser

== Installing ==
From PyPi:
 pip install gitorious-mrq-monitor

From source tree:
 python setup.py install

Note that installing is not needed to use the software.
== Usage ==

 gitorious-mrq-monitor myproject [options]

For usage from source tree, without installing:

 export PYTHONPATH=./:$PYTHONPATH
 export PATH=./bin:$PATH
 gitorious-mrq-monitor myproject [options]

== Documentation ==

 See output of
 gitorious-mrq-monitor --help

